65. An AIFI shall make general provision for standard assets at the following rates
for the funded outstanding on global loan portfolio basis:
(1) farm credit to agricultural activities, individual housing loans and Small
and Micro Enterprises (SMEs) sectors at 0.25 per cent;
(2) advances to Commercial Real Estate (CRE) sector at 1.00 per cent;
(3) advances to Commercial Real Estate - Residential Housing Sector
(CRE - RH) at 0.75 per cent;
(4) housing loans extended at teaser rates as indicated in paragraph 96;
(5) restructured advances - as stipulated in the Reserve Bank of India (All
India Financial Institutions - Resolution of Stressed Assets) Directions,
2025;
<image>
(6) All other loans and advances not included in (1) - (5) above at 0.40 per
cent.
